'''Allan Jay Silverman''' (born 1955) is an American philosopher and Professor of [[Philosophy]] at the [[Ohio State University]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Allan Silverman |url=https://philosophy.osu.edu/people/silverman.3 |website=Department of Philosophy |accessdate=31 October 2018 |language=en |date=30 June 2011}}</ref> He is also a Faculty Fellow at [[Mershon Center for International Security Studies]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Allan Silverman |url=https://philosophy.unc.edu/people/allan-silverman/ |website=Department of Philosophy |accessdate=31 October 2018}}</ref> Silverman is known for his expertise on [[ancient philosophy]].<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Burgess |first1=S. A. |title=Review of: The Dialectic of Essence. A Study of Plato's Metaphysics |journal=[[Bryn Mawr Classical Review]] |date=June 2003 |url=http://bmcr.brynmawr.edu/2003/2003-06-48.html |accessdate=31 October 2018 |issn=1055-7660}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Brouwer |first1=Mark |title=The Dialectic of Essence |journal=Ancient Philosophy |date=2007 |volume=27 |issue=1 |pages=184–190 |doi=10.5840/ancientphil200727137 |url=https://www.pdcnet.org/ancientphil/content/ancientphil_2007_0027_0001_0184_0190 |accessdate=31 October 2018 |issn=0740-2007}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Colter |first1=Robert S. |title=Review of The Dialectic of Essence: A Study of Plato's Metaphysics |journal=Notre Dame Philosophical Reviews |date=15 October 2003 |url=https://ndpr.nd.edu/news/the-dialectic-of-essence-a-study-of-plato-s-metaphysics/ |accessdate=31 October 2018 |issn=1538-1617}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Prior |first1=William J. |title=The Dialectic of Essence: A Study of Plato's Metaphysics (review) |journal=[[Journal of the History of Philosophy]] |date=2004 |volume=42 |issue=1 |pages=97–98 |doi=10.1353/hph.2004.0013 |url=https://muse.jhu.edu/article/50953 |accessdate=31 October 2018 |language=en |issn=1538-4586}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=O'Brien |first1=Denis |last2=Stern-Gillet |first2=Suzanne |title=Review of The Dialectic of Essence: A Study of Plato's Metaphysics |journal=The Philosophical Quarterly (1950-) |date=2005 |volume=55 |issue=220 |pages=507–510 |url=https://www.jstor.org/stable/pdf/3543103.pdf?seq=1#page_scan_tab_contents |accessdate=31 October 2018}}</ref>
