'''Anatol Rosenfeld''' (28 August 1912 – 11 December 1973) was a [[German Jews|Jewish-German]] philosopher and critic of arts. In 1937, fleeing the [[Nazism]], Anatol Rosenfeld emigrated to [[Brazil]] and died there, in 1973.
==Sources== * [http://www.itaucultural.org.br/aplicexternas/enciclopedia_teatro/index.cfm?fuseaction=personalidades_biografia&cd_verbete=694 Itaucultura, in Portuguese]
